 🤖 ResumeForge — AI Resume Builder

🔹 Description

ResumeForge is a dynamic web-based resume builder that allows users to create professional resumes with live preview and multiple templates.

🔹 Features

* Real-time resume preview
* Multiple templates (Modern, Minimal, Professional)
* Export resume as PDF
* Dynamic sections (Education, Projects, Skills, etc.)
* AI-powered suggestions for summaries and descriptions

🔹 Tech Stack

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript
* html2pdf.js

